title: [River's Rest, Festival Grounds]
description: A sturdy oak cart sits near the pathway, shaded by an oilcloth umbrella in an alarming shade of bright green.  From the umbrella's pole hangs a sign with large painted words that read, "Fried Pickle Chips!"
A sturdy oak cart sits near the pathway, with a closed umbrella sitting nearby.  Draped from the front of the cart is a sign illuminated by torchlight, which reads, "Fried Pickle Chips!"
